name: SEE WHAT I SEE
description:
Welcome to See What I See.

A 2D single player game created by Fred the fred and ██████ in 20XX.

STORY

You wake up in a place you don't know. You try to open your eyes, but everything is still dark. You try to scream but you can't either. Suddenly a blue face appears in front of your eyes. It tells you that you have been kidnapped, but they are not going to kill you, for now. They give you a chance to survive, if you play a game.

RULES

You are in a house that has 25 rooms, right now you are in one of them. Each room has a camera, except the room you are in right now. You will have to watch the cameras to see the rooms you are not in. You can mark with an X the rooms where you know for sure that you are not there. If you fail, you will be killed by someone you can't see either.

LEVELS

The game consists of 11 levels. Each one with a feature that will make it more difficult than the previous level.
